# Harness Lite (in-repo)

Implementation lives in `tools/harness/`. Orchestrator entry: `spine harness <subcommand>`.

## Wave order (ADR-008)

1. **Audit** — deterministic scanners only (`spine harness audit`)
2. **Fix** — one wave, exclusive file scope (`harness-fix-wave` skill)
3. **Verify** — charter evals + optional QA (`spine harness verify --run-qa`)

Never mix audit and fix in the same wave.

## Commands

```bash
bash tools/harness/dogfood.sh
bash tools/harness/spine-harness status --markdown
bash tools/harness/spine-harness audit --project . --all
bash tools/harness/spine-harness verify --project . --run-qa
```

## Skills

- `harness-orchestrator` — loop / gate coordination
- `harness-audit-wave`, `harness-fix-wave`, `harness-verify-wave`
- `spine-harness-session` — PM check-in + session bookends

Spec: `Handoff.md`
